# VPN Tunnel Monitoring

## Overview

Built an Ansible-based monitoring solution that checks VPN tunnel connectivity and automatically alerts on outages.

## Technologies

- Ansible
- YAML
- Ubuntu Linux
- OpenVPN
- Semaphore

## Features

- Tunnel status monitoring
- Email notifications
- State tracking
- Automatic recovery attempts

## Skills Demonstrated

- Network troubleshooting
- Linux administration
- Infrastructure automation
- YAML development

